00:42:32.730 --> 00:42:36.550
The Archie Green Fellowship enabled
us to focus on people employed

00:42:36.550 --> 00:42:40.560
in small businesses and trades
who have specialized skills.

00:42:40.560 --> 00:42:43.920
Two of the field workers had
