00:42:51.290 --> 00:42:54.140
One reason that I chose them
is that they had no experience

00:42:54.140 --> 00:42:56.300
in Louisiana or even the south.

00:42:56.300 --> 00:43:00.300
So they came with little to no
preconceived ideas about the city.

00:43:00.300 --> 00:43:03.220
This fresh perspective
was significant

00:43:03.220 --> 00:43:05.070
