01:51:55.830 --> 01:51:58.280
And that's, of course, the two kind

01:51:58.280 --> 01:52:01.420
of central tenets of
working in archives.

01:52:01.420 --> 01:52:07.380
You have to gather the
materials and preserve them

01:52:07.380 --> 01:52:09.490
and you have to create access.

01:52:09.490 --> 01:52:12.450
And we work with that every day.

01:52:12.450 --> 01:52:20.230 position:56%
In 1932 or so, the Archive of
American Folk Song, as it was called

01:52:20.230 --> 01:52:26.240
