01:56:25.530 --> 01:56:29.810
I am the curator of linguistics
at the National Museum

01:56:29.810 --> 01:56:31.940
of Natural History in the
Anthropology Department.

01:56:31.940 --> 01:56:34.510
And I'm also the director
