They're engaging with
you when you're shooting.

02:04:33.240 --> 02:04:34.540
It can be a dance.

02:04:34.540 --> 02:04:36.300
They're not going to
show you the steps,

02:04:36.300 --> 02:04:38.750
they're going to dance for you.

02:04:38.750 --> 02:04:42.410
On people when we do the civil
rights oral history interviews,

02:04:42.410 --> 02:04:44.840 position:56%
we're not just getting a story told.

02:04:44.840 --> 02:04:47.520
They are performing
the story for us.

02:04:47.520 --> 02:04:54.270
And the resulting tape is
a glimpse into that moment

02:04:54.270 --> 02:04:56.510
when this information was shared.

02:04:56.510 --> 02:04:58.710
There's a lot more valence to it

02:04:58.710 --> 02:05:02.140
than just what can be
abstracted from the words.

02:05:02.140 --> 02:05:07.720
And I just wanted to mention that
as something that should be kept

02:05:07.720 --> 02:05:11.260
in mind that it's very
easy when you're--

02:05:11.260 --> 02:05:14.350
what it used to be now with the--
now I just use my cellphone.

02:05:14.350 --> 02:05:17.850
But in the olden days when
you were on photographing

02:05:17.850 --> 02:05:22.720 position:56%
with like they're doing in the back,
it's easy to get lost up and swept

02:05:22.720 --> 02:05:28.020
up in your technology,
you know, your craft.

02:05:28.020 --> 02:05:33.060
And in the kind of work we all
do, it's much more important

02:05:33.060 --> 02:05:36.830 position:56%
to nail the craft before you go out.

02:05:36.830 --> 02:05:40.570
Know how to get it into focus,
make a nice composition.

02:05:40.570 --> 02:05:44.050
And then you're engaged--
You as a crafts person,

02:05:44.050 --> 02:05:47.510
you're actually engaged in a
communication with the person.

02:05:47.510 --> 02:05:52.000
On the oral history
interviews, we'd-- We have--

02:05:52.000 --> 02:05:55.940
usually just myself
and the oral historian.

02:05:55.940 --> 02:06:04.930
And it's a relationship
in those two hours.

02:06:04.930 --> 02:06:13.360 position:56%
Another point I'd like to make about
shooting for documentary projects is

02:06:13.360 --> 02:06:17.720
