02:06:23.680 --> 02:06:27.720
in a pyramid in the desert.

02:06:27.720 --> 02:06:30.000
And other times though
like I see the--

02:06:30.000 --> 02:06:32.990
like I can see it being used
a little bit of stock footage.

02:06:32.990 --> 02:06:38.280
