02:07:10.720 --> 02:07:14.060
Because in this case,
we're building a tapestry,

02:07:14.060 --> 02:07:17.790
the documentation is
building an enormous tapestry

02:07:17.790 --> 02:07:22.400
of a huge historical event.

02:07:22.400 --> 02:07:26.730
The other point I'd
like to make is just

02:07:26.730 --> 02:07:32.090
to give a hundred thousand
props to the Library of Congress

02:07:32.090 --> 02:07:38.270
