So anyone can access it live

02:07:44.270 --> 02:07:47.400
and they can feel what
people are saying.

02:07:47.400 --> 02:07:51.990
They can read the transcript and
get into abstract information

02:07:51.990 --> 02:07:53.570
or to find where they are.

02:07:53.570 --> 02:07:57.740
This is something that's now
technologically possible.

02:07:57.740 --> 02:08:03.050
And this is the first time I've
been involved in something that--

02:08:03.050 --> 02:08:08.910 position:56%
thanks to Guha Shankar who actually
done-- and actually makes it happen.

02:08:08.910 --> 02:08:12.200
First time in my life that that
material I haven't had to wait

02:08:12.200 --> 02:08:18.470
for a year or two or whatever
before things can circulate or--

02:08:18.470 --> 02:08:27.440 position:56%
And these enterprises we are
engaged in or done at great expense,

02:08:27.440 --> 02:08:31.140
great financial expense
and great personal expense.

02:08:31.140 --> 02:08:34.950
There's a lot of effort
that goes into it.

02:08:34.950 --> 02:08:42.740
And it's extremely gratifying
to see it actually being seen.

02:08:42.740 --> 02:08:46.010
So I'll let someone else
